1.0 (unreleased)
-----------------
- Added optimized kernel library for X86_64/SSE
- Multithreading at work group granularity using pthreads.
- Tries to figure out the optimal maximum number of
  threads for the system. Currently works only in Linux 
  using the /proc/cpuinfo interface.
- Preliminary support for ARM architectures on Linux.
- Barrier handling finished. Barriers inside for-loops etc.
  now supported.
- Support for automatic local variables.

